No Time For Appearances Of Life

All one politician had to do - for the sake of 8 billion others - is lie about THEMSELVES! once;  and lose that election;  and say;  "We lied.  You could have - there was nothing to the authority claiming any need or right otherwise - built a house, with his name on it, and put a sign out "just for" - when he's able to, and there are empty homes, abandoned for a season or all time... without his name on it, and as close as surely, legally for him to enter".  He has no money though, too, for food.  It will kind of then be a policy, very tiny ones, not the half million dollar sheds in the right places on the shore.  We'll get over this - cash - someday, somehow, that much, without bothering types of people.  I think we were educated enough to, even the communes - we had the education and the comfort of love at that point, then, and should have, and still can.  It's not that bad yet.  It might be if we don't.  It's God's way.  It's his way.  He is that good.  He changes things.  It would be for the better then.

The sea will sing.  It won't be conceivably beautiful, if it were done.  the parts of the universe just clicking at so small an almost dead rate, now;  could live;  this little speck doesn't have to go it along under science without the things heaven wants for it/us.  all.  Pray for Stormy;  that - she, returns from the abuse, that awful thing where she lives.
